text: Wayne Snyman (born 8 March 1985 in Welkom)Profile at Sports-Reference.com is a South African race walker. At the 2016 Summer Olympics, he competed in the Men’s 20 km walk. He finished in 58th place with a time of 1:29:20. In 2019, he competed in the men's 20 kilometres walk at the 2019 World Athletics Championships held in Doha, Qatar.
